4) Auk, 111 (1), pp. 63-69; Svensson, L., Identification Guide to European Passerines (1992) Heraclio Fournier SA, p. 184; Thorup, K., Tottrup, A.P., Rahbek, C., Patterns of phenological changes in migratory birds (2007) Oecologica, 151, pp. 697-703; Woodrey, M.S., Moore, F.R., Age-related differences in the stopover of fall lanbird migrants on the coast of Alabama (1997) Auk, 114 (4), pp. 695-707; Young D.P. JR, Resource defense by a migrating song sparrow (1988) Journal of Field Ornithology, 61 (2), pp. 232-236","Miholcsa, T.; Eötvös Loránd University, Department General Biology, Pázmány sétány 1/C, 1117 Budapest, Hungary; email: mihhok@gmail.com",,,,,,,,12178837,,,,"English","Acta. Zool. Acad. Sci. Hung.",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-70349206176
